  "body": "#### System information\r\nerigon version 2021.08.3-alpha\r\nOS & Version: Linux\r\nCommit hash : e7574a6d14a64c5af58574d909b8c6a014bd2daf\r\n\r\n#### Expected behaviour\r\nTransaction object returned by `eth_getTransactionByHash` should include raw transaction data (field `raw`). Not sure if this is really part of the specification, but OE includes the raw transaction data for both pending and mined txs. See here, section \"Transaction Responses\":\r\nhttps://openethereum.github.io/JSONRPC\r\n\r\n#### Actual behaviour\r\nNo raw transaction data is returned by `eth_getTransactionByHash`.\r\n",
